      <title>据《金融时报》报道，Axel Springer 与 KKR 接近达成 135 亿欧元分拆协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-14/axel-springer-and-kkr-near-deal-on-13-5-billion-breakup-ft</link>
